== 安全漏洞 ==
2014年5月，繼[[OpenSSL|OpenSSL]]漏洞後，開源安全軟件再曝安全漏洞。新加坡南洋理工大學研究人員王晶發現，[[OAuth|OAuth]]2.0和[[OpenID|OpenID]]授權接口的網站存隱蔽重定向漏洞、英文名為“Covert Redirect”。該漏洞OSVDB編號106567<ref>{{cite web|title=OAuth / OpenID Unspecified Application Redirect Weakness|url=http://www.osvdb.org/show/osvdb/106567|publisher=OSVDB. 5月02 2014}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。SCIP編號vuldb.13185<ref>{{cite web|title=VulDB: OAuth/OpenID 2.0 privilege escalation|url=http://www.scip.ch/en/?vuldb.13185|publisher=SCIP. 5月12 2014|access-date=2014-11-08|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315221901/http://www.scip.ch/en/?vuldb.13185|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中国國家信息安全漏洞共享平臺編號CNVD-2014-02785<ref>{{cite web |title=OAuth 2.0隱蔽重定向漏洞 |url=http://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/CNVD-2014-02785 |publisher=國家信息安全漏洞共享平臺. 5月06 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108172656/http://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/CNVD-2014-02785 |archivedate=2014-11-08 }}</ref>。Bugtraq ID是67196<ref name="securityfocus">{{cite web | url=http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/67196 | title=OAuth and OpenID Open Redirection Vulnerability | publisher=SecurityFocus | date=2 May 2014 | accessdate=15 November 2014 | archive-date=2021-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122034048/https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/67196/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

該漏洞首先由[[CNET|CNET]]報道<ref>{{cite web |title=Serious security flaw in OAuth, OpenID discovered |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/serious-security-flaw-in-oauth-and-openid-discovered/ |publisher=CNET. 5月02 2014 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151102002904/http://www.cnet.com/news/serious-security-flaw-in-oauth-and-openid-discovered/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並由此引起廣泛關註和大量討論。雅虎，福克斯新聞，黑客新聞，鳳凰網，人民網等媒體認為該漏洞影響很大<ref>{{cite web |title=Facebook, Google users threatened by new security flaw |url=http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2014/05/05/facebook-google-users-threatened-by-new-security-flaw/ |publisher=福克斯新聞. 5月05 2014 |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924164243/http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2014/05/05/facebook-google-users-threatened-by-new-security-flaw/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Nasty Covert Redirect Vulnerability found in OAuth and OpenID |url=http://thehackernews.com/2014/05/nasty-covert-redirect-vulnerability.html |publisher=Thehackernews. 5月03 2014 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108170413/http://thehackernews.com/2014/05/nasty-covert-redirect-vulnerability.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=OAuth與OpenID登錄工具曝出重大漏洞 |url=http://digi.163.com/14/0503/08/9RACJBK900162OUT.html |publisher=網易. 5月03 2014 |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108102054/http://digi.163.com/14/0503/08/9RACJBK900162OUT.html |archive-date=2014-11-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=兩款互聯網登錄系統曝出重大漏洞短期內或無法修復 |url=http://media.sohu.com/20140504/n399096249.shtml |publisher=搜狐. 5月04 2014 |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108101341/http://media.sohu.com/20140504/n399096249.shtml |archive-date=2014-11-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=OAuth和OpenID兩款登六系統再曝重大漏洞 |url=http://network.pconline.com.cn/471/4713896.html |publisher=太平洋電腦網. 5月04 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108100217/http://network.pconline.com.cn/471/4713896.html |archivedate=2014-11-08 }}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite web |title=Oauth2.0協議曝漏洞大量社交網隱私或遭泄露 |url=http://it.people.com.cn/n/2014/0504/c1009-24969253.html |publisher=人民網. 5月04 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108131652/http://it.people.com.cn/n/2014/0504/c1009-24969253.html |archivedate=2014-11-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=OAuth與OpenID登錄工具曝出重大漏洞 |url=http://www.csdn.net/article/2014-05-04/2819588 |publisher=CSDN. 5月04 2014 |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721180420/http://www.csdn.net/article/2014-05-04/2819588 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。攻擊者創建一個使用真實站點地址的彈出式登錄窗口——而不是使用一個假的域名——以引誘上網者輸入他們的個人信息。而Mashable等則認為該漏洞是個舊漏洞<ref name="Mashable">{{cite web | url=http://mashable.com/2014/05/02/oauth-openid-not-new-heartbleed/ | title=Another Security Flaw Gets the Heartbleed Treatment, But Don't Believe the Hype | publisher=Tetraph | date=3 May 2014 | accessdate=10 November 2014 | archive-date=2021-03-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327213737/https://mashable.com/2014/05/02/oauth-openid-not-new-heartbleed/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

最後的主流結論是，隱蔽重定向是一個值得註意的漏洞。該漏洞達不到[[HeartBleed|HeartBleed]]的級別，但仍然是對授權應用權限的一個提醒<ref>{{cite web |title=Covert Redirect Flaw in OAuth is Not the Next Heartbleed |url=http://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/covert-redirect-flaw-oauth-not-next-heartbleed |publisher=Symantec. May 03 2014 |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612182748/https://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/covert-redirect-flaw-oauth-not-next-heartbleed |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ScMagazine">{{cite web | url=http://www.scmagazine.com/covert-redirect-vulnerability-impacts-oauth-20-openid/article/345407/ | title='Covert Redirect' vulnerability impacts OAuth 2.0, OpenID | publisher=SC Magazine | date=2 May 2014 | accessdate=10 November 2014 | archive-date=2016-03-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317055659/http://www.scmagazine.com/covert-redirect-vulnerability-impacts-oauth-20-openid/article/345407/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

OAuth和OpenID也分別對此漏洞進行了說明和建議<ref>{{cite web |title=OAuth Security Advisory: 2014.1 "Covert Redirect" |url=http://oauth.net/advisories/2014-1-covert-redirect/ |publisher=OAuth. 5月04 2014 |accessdate=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121111134/http://oauth.net/advisories/2014-1-covert-redirect/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Covert Redirect |url=http://openid.net/2014/05/15/covert-redirect/ |publisher=OpenID. 5月15 2014 |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2014-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020125911/http://openid.net/2014/05/15/covert-redirect/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

